<h1>Flottec Network of <br>Global Alliance Partners</h1>
<p>
Flottec is committed to providing our customers with strong local support in partnership with leading regional and global service providers, distributors, and manufacturers. <br><br>Our network of alliance partners were specifically created for their capabilities to work together with Flottec to supply high quality products, innovative technology, superior flotation application expertise, onsite service and 100% delivery reliability everywhere in the world. <br><br>Our worldwide partners include:</p>
<p><span class="bold">Productos Quimicos Flottec</span><br>Located in San Luis Potosi, Mexico. <br><br>
<span class="bold">Chemiqa</span><br> 
A joint venture between Flottec and Milman Company located in Sudbury Canada. <br><br>

<span class="bold">Kemtec</span><br> 
A joint Venture between Flottec and Sinoz located in Melbourne Australia. <br><br>

<span class="bold">Florrea</span><br> 
Located in Shengyang, China. <br><br>

<span class="bold">Metrix</span><br>A joint venture between Flottec and Bluecoast Technologies located in Parksville, BC Canada.
</p>

